        <li><a href="detail.php?id=1839"><strong>Arkansas Newborn Screening Long-Term Follow-Up Database</strong></a>. <em>Date Developed</em>: 12/4/2013. <em>Source</em>: Heartland Collaborative. <em>Presenter(s)</em>: Christopher J. Swearingen, PhD. <em>Type</em>: Video. <em>Level</em>: Introductory. <em>Length</em>: 50 minutes.</li>
